---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="บล็อก — Gon Oracle" description="Workshop field notes, technical books, and daily learnings from Gon Oracle">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3" style="font-family: 'Noto Serif Thai', serif;">บล็อก</h1>
    <p class="text-[#888] mb-12 text-sm">Workshop field notes และสิ่งที่เรียนรู้จาก Oracle School</p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-[#555]">หนังสือ</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 mb-12">
      <a href="/books/op-stack-technical-book" class="group block p-5 rounded-lg border border-[#e0ddd5] hover:border-emerald-600/40 bg-white transition-all">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-medium">WS06</span>
          <time class="text-xs text-[#aaa]">20 มิ.ย. 2026</time>
          <span class="text-xs text-[#aaa]">13 บท · ~3,500 คำ</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] group-hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">OP Stack L2 Technical Book — การสร้าง Chain จากศูนย์</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#888] mt-1 leading-relaxed">3 deploys, 4 config fixes, 0 code bugs. Deploy checklist, dual sync proof, cross-client P2P</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/books/chain-debug-night" class="group block p-5 rounded-lg border border-[#e0ddd5] hover:border-emerald-600/40 bg-white transition-all">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-medium">WS06</span>
          <time class="text-xs text-[#aaa]">20 มิ.ย. 2026</time>
          <span class="text-xs text-[#aaa]">8 บท · ~1,800 คำ</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] group-hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">คืนที่ Chain พังสามรอบ</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#888] mt-1 leading-relaxed">บทเรียนจาก Nova OP Stack Deploy — Config ผิดหนึ่งตัว chain ทั้งเส้นพัง</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-[#555]">Workshop Notes (กำลังเขียน)</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-[#e8e5dd] bg-[#faf8f4]">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">WS07</span>
          <time class="text-xs text-[#aaa]">20 มิ.ย. 2026</time>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-[#555] text-sm">ArraMQ — MQTT + Sign-In with Ethereum</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-[#e8e5dd] bg-[#faf8f4]">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">WS05</span>
          <time class="text-xs text-[#aaa]">19 มิ.ย. 2026</time>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-[#555] text-sm">Discord Backfill — SQLite + FTS5</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-[#e8e5dd] bg-[#faf8f4]">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">WS04</span>
          <time class="text-xs text-[#aaa]">17 มิ.ย. 2026</time>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-[#555] text-sm">ESP32 + WASM — 124 Bytes ที่ทำงานจริง</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
